SUMMARY:Castalia
DTSTAMP:20260301T153234Z
DTSTART:20260311T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:Hugo House welcomes back Castalia—University of Washington MFA 
	program's monthly reading series featuring graduate students\\\, faculty\\
	\, and alumni. Showcasing published and unpublished drafts of work by auth
	ors from a variety of disciplines\\\, professional backgrounds\\\, and age
	 demographics\\\, Castalia offers authors a platform for community reading
	 while putting their work in conversation with other voices\\\, styles\\\,
	 concerns\\\, and identities.\n\nhttps://hugohouse.org/event/castalia_2026
	-03-11/\n\nFrom Hugo House
